{"tid":1149818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇貞昌稱「香港淪陷」 港客帶肉入台可罰25萬","createTime":"2019-05-11T11:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T11:53:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"831f676ac9f13536700d73fe699e51db2a631466","tid":1149818,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190511/_2019051117565018640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190511%2F_2019051117565018640.jpg&h=95734216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n針對香港上水屠房有來自大陸豬內樣本驗出非洲豬瘟病毒，台灣的行政院長蘇貞昌在Facebook專頁表示，非洲豬瘟疫情蔓延「香港淪陷」，港澳旅客入境，已比照中國大陸旅客，將執行百分之百檢查行李，為守護台灣滷肉飯，請大家多配合、多留意。<br />\n<br />\n蘇貞昌指出，非洲豬瘟疫情蔓延，再次提醒到台的港澳旅客，以及出入港澳地區的台灣民眾，台灣從今年1月16日起，進行全面檢查手提行李，且各地入境關卡增購26台X光機。<br />\n<br />\n蘇貞昌表示，只要從疫區帶肉品入境台灣，一律開罰新台幣20萬元(折合約5.07萬港元) 、再犯就罰100萬元(折合約25.3萬港元) ，外籍旅客不繳清罰款就不得入境。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的行政院農業委員會副主委黃金城說，黃金城表示，香港主要豬肉來源來自中國大陸地區，因此針對香港旅客的邊境管制，早已經拉到與中國大陸旅客來台的同樣層級，包含手提及託運行李都要百分百經過X光檢查，若被查獲私帶疫區肉品也會處罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190511/_2019051117564913042.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190511%2F_2019051117564913042.jpg&h=e3f359f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1498423/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1498423%2F&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUGiIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=40faa040\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1498423%2F&h=bc4d55b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1498423/</a>"},{"pid":"dab58bbac8fb54f8eb02cb3348d6bc8d000cab29","tid":1149818,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"大把北區垃圾廢中幫大陸走私都冇人捉啦<br />\n<br />\n港豬食病豬啦 好味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}